1. 创建docker image
docker build -t ubuntu-dev:20.04 -f Dockerfile .

2. 查看image
docker images

3. 创建container; 将主机/home/zhengminyou/docker22.04/workspace/挂载到docker的/workspace下
docker run -it \
  --name monolanemapping \
  -v /home/zhengminyou/docker22.04/workspace/:/workspace:rw \
  -w /workspace \
  --user 1000:1000 \
  ubuntu-dev:20.04
  
  4. 停止容器
  docker stop <container-id|name>
  
  删除容器
  docker rm <container-id|name>
  
  删除镜像
  docker rmi <image-id|repo:tag>
  
  启动docker
  docker restart 92aa72ba9aa5 && docker exec -it 92aa72ba9aa5 /bin/bash
  
 5. 利用已有的docker，新建docker
 
 5.1 将当前容器（包括你在里面做的所有更改）保存为一个新的镜像：
 docker commit monolanemapping monolanemapping-with-x11:latest

 5.2 添加配置，新建docker
 docker run -it \
  --gpus all \
  -v /etc/localtime:/etc/localtime:ro \
  -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix:rw \
  -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY \
  -e NVIDIA_DRIVER_CAPABILITIES=all \
  -e GDK_SCALE \
  -e GDK_DPI_SCALE \
  --name monolanemapping-new \
  -v /home/zhengminyou/docker22.04/workspace/:/workspace:rw \
  -w /workspace \
  --user 1000:1000 \
  monolanemapping-with-x11:latest
  
  docker run -it \
